## Summary

1. **Inputs**: Manus narrative (required), Manus competitor landscape (required), Pain signals (optional), JTBD (optional)
2. **Tasks**: Identify niche size/psychographics/subcultures, extract vocabulary/identity/cultural norms, map communities, extract frustrations/desires/worldview, identify entry points, document niche segmentation, identify adjacent niches
